Every resident of Kalmykia is a debtor
Residents of the Republic increasingly visit the official website of the Federal bailiff service of Russia in Kazakhstan.
According to the specialists of the Department of organizational and control work, information and information security of the Republican Department, over the past eight months, more than 140 thousand visits to the site itself, more than 42 thousand - the section "data Bank of enforcement proceedings", 661 payment receipts for payment of debts were downloaded.
According to the Chairman of the Public Council at the UFSSP of Russia in Kazakhstan Valery Bogdanov, almost every resident of the region has debts for utilities, traffic fines, Bank loans, loans, and no one is immune from unforeseen situations.
But debtors can expect negative consequences in the form of, for example, a ban on travel abroad.
That is why the FSSP of Russia in Kazakhstan recommends to all who have planned a trip abroad, to clarify in the Department of bailiffs at the place of residence or on the website www.r08fssprus.ru information about the presence of unpaid debts and repay them.
The service has created a "data Bank of enforcement proceedings" for the convenience of citizens.
This special electronic application is available not only on the regional sites of the FSSP of Russia, but also in social networks and mobile devices iPad, iPhone and smartphone.
In the data Bank contains information on enforcement proceedings initiated Kalmyk police officers in respect of all debtors, explains the assistant head of UFSSP Rossii po RK Delger Bodaeva.
"In the presence of debts, the system displays information about the number and date of initiation of enforcement proceedings; the name of the body that issued the writ of execution or other act; its number, amount and type of debt; the address of the bailiff Department; the name of the bailiff; contact phone number.
Information on the course of enforcement proceedings can also be obtained on the portal of public services at: http://epgu.gosuslugi.ru"
